<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🤖 智能助手 - GUCCANG</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/assistant.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 返回导航 -->
    <div class="nav-back">
        <a href="/main" class="back-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i> 返回主页
        </a>
        <a href="/mcp" class="back-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-tools"></i> MCP管理
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <header class="assistant-header">
            <div class="assistant-title">
                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                <h1>智能助手</h1>
                <span class="status-indicator online">在线</span>
            </div>
            <div class="assistant-subtitle">
                <p>您的个人数据分析师和生活教练</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="assistant-main">
            <!-- 左侧：聊天界面 -->
            <section class="chat-section">
                <div class="chat-container">
                    <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
                        <!-- 欢迎消息 -->
                        <div class="message assistant-message">
                            <div class="avatar">
                                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="message-content">
                                <div class="message-text">
                                    <p>您好！我是您的智能助手，现在配备了强大的MCP工具支持！</p>
                                    <p>我可以帮您：</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>📊 使用MCP工具分析您的个人数据和行为模式</li>
                                        <li>💡 基于工具调用提供个性化的建议和提醒</li>
                                        <li>📋 通过工具集成帮助管理任务和计划</li>
                                        <li>📈 调用外部工具生成各种统计报告</li>
                                        <li>🎯 使用专业工具追踪目标进度和成就</li>
                                        <li>🔧 <strong>新功能：智能工具调用</strong> - 根据需求自动选择合适的MCP工具</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>试试问我："使用MCP工具帮我分析最近的数据"或"调用工具帮我优化时间分配"</p>
                                    <p><em>提示：您可以在右侧工具面板中选择特定的MCP工具，或让我自动选择最合适的工具。</em></p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="message-time">刚刚</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="chat-input-container">
                        <div class="quick-actions">
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="status">📊 状态分析</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="time">⏰ 时间分析</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="goals">🎯 目标进度</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="suggestions">💡 智能建议</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="tools" onclick="showMCPToolsDialog()">🔧 工具</button>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="input-wrapper">
                            <input type="text" id="messageInput" placeholder="问问我任何关于您的数据或计划的问题..." maxlength="500">
                            <button class="send-btn" id="sendBtn">
                                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 右侧：智能面板 -->
            <aside class="info-panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 数据概览</h3>
                    <button class="refresh-btn" id="refreshData">
                        <i class="fas fa-refresh"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <!-- 今日概览 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i> 今日概览</h4>
                    <div class="stats-grid">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayTasks">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">任务完成</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayReading">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">阅读时间</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayExercise">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">锻炼记录</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayBlogs">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">博客写作</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 智能建议 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> 智能建议</h4>
                    <div class="suggestions-list" id="suggestionsList">
                        <div class="suggestion-item">
                            <div class="suggestion-icon">💡</div>
                            <div class="suggestion-text">正在分析您的数据...</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 快速操作 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> 快速操作</h4>
                    <div class="quick-operations">
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="new-task">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> 新建任务
                        </button>
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="record-exercise">
                            <i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i> 记录锻炼
                        </button>
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="write-blog">
                            <i class="fas fa-pen"></i> 写博客
                        </button>
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="add-reading">
                            <i class="fas fa-book"></i> 添加阅读
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 趋势图表 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-area"></i> 近期趋势</h4>
                    <div class="chart-container">
                        <canvas id="trendChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </main>

        <!-- MCP工具管理大面板 -->
        <section class="mcp-tools-panel">
            <div class="mcp-tools-panel-header">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> MCP 工具管理中心</h3>
                <div class="mcp-tools-panel-actions">
                    <button class="mcp-panel-toggle" onclick="toggleMCPPanel()">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mcp-tools-panel-content" id="mcp-tools-panel-content">
                <div id="mcp-tools-status-large" class="mcp-tools-status-large">
                    <div class="mcp-status-loading">
                        <i class="fas fa-spinner fa-spin"></i>
                        <span>正在加载MCP工具...</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mcp-info-large">
                    <div class="mcp-info-grid">
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>工具选择</strong>
                                <p>选择要在对话中使用的MCP工具。未选择时将使用所有可用工具。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>服务器状态</strong>
                                <p>实时显示各个MCP服务器的连接状态和可用工具数量。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>搜索功能</strong>
                                <p>支持按工具名称、服务器或描述进行快速搜索和过滤。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>配置管理</strong>
                                <p>可前往<a href="/mcp">MCP配置页面</a>管理服务器和工具配置。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 设置面板 -->
        <div class="settings-panel" id="settingsPanel">
            <div class="settings-header">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> 助手设置</h3>
                <button class="close-btn" id="closeSettings">
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="settings-content">
                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>通知设置</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label class="switch">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="enableNotifications" checked>
                            <span class="slider"></span>
                        </label>
                        <span>启用智能提醒</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label class="switch">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="enableSuggestions" checked>
                            <span class="slider"></span>
                        </label>
                        <span>显示智能建议</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>分析深度</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label>分析时间范围:</label>
                        <select id="analysisRange">
                            <option value="7">最近7天</option>
                            <option value="30" selected>最近30天</option>
                            <option value="90">最近90天</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>个性化</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label>助手人格:</label>
                        <select id="assistantPersonality">
                            <option value="friendly">友好温和</option>
                            <option value="professional" selected>专业严谨</option>
                            <option value="encouraging">鼓励激励</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 设置按钮 -->
        <button class="settings-btn" id="settingsBtn">
            <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
        </button>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/assistant.js"></script>
</body>
</html>